    lightgbm,
    rBayesianOptimization,
    modeldata,
    Rfast,
    rmarkdown,
    rsample,
    sparsevctrs,
    testthat,
    tibble,
    yardstick,
    xgboost
NeedsCompilation: yes
ByteCompile: true
SystemRequirements: Dedicated Linux/HPC host recommended: Intel Xeon Platinum 8260-class CPU, high-memory NUMA server, LightGBM runtime plus optional XGBoost runtime. Optional external Limbo ask/tell executable configured via TBTB_LIMBO_COMMAND.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
